{"tid":314123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭開會6小時　要官員多聽民意","createTime":"2017-07-09T02:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T13:37:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4b1722d573b2f89bfb98f38eb23f0db2951f2f","tid":314123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:04:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083602&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083602%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&d=9K4m331hoOOF5Vr9VFkABaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4026e11f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083602%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&h=319be5dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083602&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭開會6小時　要官員多聽民意<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n林鄭昨與問責官員舉行集思會，並上載自拍照片到社交網。林鄭facebook圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥上任踏入第二星期，林鄭昨與一眾問責官員舉行集思會，據了解林鄭在會上談及她的施政理念、要求問責官員要有團隊精神，多落區聽取民意及不能忽略地區小事，又責成官員要改善行政立法關係，加強與立法會議員溝通。<br />\n<br />\n冀與立會議員溝通<br />\n<br />\n林鄭昨於社交網發文並上載照片，與一眾問責官員在禮賓府召開集思會，林鄭更以「與團隊跳出office」形容會議。據知除外訪的財政司司長陳茂波未能出席，政務司司長張建宗、律政司司長袁國強及13名局長、特首辦主任陳國基，均有出席，會議長達6小時，在10月施政報告前仍會再有類似集思會。<br />\n據知林鄭期望新班子多與立會議員溝通，盡早邀請議員參與討論，改善行政立法關係，又求官員要有團隊協作，政策局要盡早就跨部門事宜達成共識，更要求官員要勤政愛民，不應只着眼大事而忽略小事，又舉例稱，就算小事如社區增加洗手間，問責官員要兼顧和解決，並要多聽地區人士意見，同時也要友善面對傳媒，給予傳媒所需資訊。<br />\n■記者莫劍弦<br />\n<br />\n林鄭新班子逐個睇<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/hkcabinet￼\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fhkcabinet%EF%BF%BC&d=9K4m331hoOOF5Vr9VFkABaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ffb95ed0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/hkcabinet￼</a>"},{"pid":"d2af79fece337252558c11c13c3f95a4d399a7d8","tid":314123,"uid":112308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:10:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，閉門開會點聽民意，夠疆唔帶黑警去街市買餸，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f8f3aa2800aeb2152f543d89cafaf1e23b058a","tid":314123,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:11:23.000Z","msg":"cy2.0"},{"pid":"accf43fe602d85472355f15f13145f670f266672","tid":314123,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:19:49.000Z","msg":"有你講無人講，聽完打官腔敷衍你果隻聽?"},{"pid":"8aac8b4430ef14d7d5ef7011ea260f7073967782","tid":314123,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有你講無人講，聽完打官腔敷衍你果隻聽?</blockquote><br />\n大家都可以講，講完林太就會話「我將會xxx，打算xxxx」，大家嘅意見可以收皮喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bd34b803db6e1f9560302dd9429b6e07d2ceee","tid":314123,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"好似雜種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2514c7ffb618c5ac62987ffbca0e69619a92283","tid":314123,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d07df89b466e9d7cb2a2cfcf6196aa71cf222218","tid":314123,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"呢期喪做門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇多半年咩料先"},{"pid":"5261bc9c255c2dba76cbb6d32f58af6143622d0c","tid":314123,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢期喪做門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇多半年咩料先</blockquote><br />\n扮老曾"},{"pid":"8692fe2ef